_sText:
We present you a huge update for ba_jail_electric_vip_v2 with xmas/new year recolor. 
This is the latest refurbished and optimised version of "electric" series. 

There are 13 minigames here on the map. 

Here is the list: 
❄ Frozen Pool 
❄ High Diving 
❄ Snowy Yard 
❄ Seven Colors 
❄ Shot4shot Room 
❄ Race - Snowy Skipping 
❄ Crazy Snowman 
❄ Cold Kitchen 
❄ Chairs 
❄ Ice Soccer 
❄ Disco 
❄ Ice Escape 
❄ Secret room 

Other notes: 
❄ Map has been balanced for both T and CT play with some CT teleports and new aisles. 
❄ All cells have the breakable ice effect atm while being opened. 
❄ You can also break the ice cell door using the knife stab (approx. 1,5 min). 
❄ Watch our YouTube video to explore all the secrets!

Credits: energetic $@@@time!
